images.prompt: Amidst a swirling cosmos where black opal hues meld seamlessly with the ethereal glow of rose-tinted light, a resplendent sun archangel soars above an industrial landscape, its majestic wings illuminated by a cascade of melting neon, casting intricate shadows that dance across the gears and pipes of a sprawling dieselpunk world, while overhead, an abstract perspective reveals the intricate interplay of technology and divine essence, all punctuated by a captivating lens flare that adds an otherworldly shimmer, inviting the viewer to immerse themselves in this vibrant tapestry of light and machine, where the boundaries of the celestial and the mechanical intertwine in a symphony of color and form.
